717756f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 156th Street
717756f-a.text:
Broadway, east side, south from West 158th to 156th Streets, showing
prominently the 10-story Columbus Apartments at the S.E. corner of
157th Street. Also note at that point, a subway station entrance.
About 1914.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
